  "body": "# Problem\nPairing code could contain capital [L] and lower case [i] which look identical to the user therefore pairing code could be hard to guess.\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/57301523-ee54d400-70e1-11e9-8b69-a279b56fc8e0.png)\n\n## Steps\n\n\n1. open status\n1. tap create new account\n1. select keycard\n1. hold the card until app generates your keys\n\n## Details\nSome doc here : https://status.im/keycard_api/apdu_init.html\n\nhttps://stackoverflow.com/questions/55556/characters-to-avoid-in-automatically-generated-passwords could be helpful\n\n## Notes\n@guylouis @hesterbruikman i feel like this could be a bad user experience since user will think that our app is not working\n\n@andmironov maybe you know other symbols which could be confusing and should be excluded due this reason ? Thanks!\n\n",
